ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:56:17.000Z","msg":"(綜合報道)(星島日報報道)肩負香港治安重任的新任警務處處長盧偉聰今天接棒，他作風低調，外界對其成長路所知甚少，經本報深入了解，原來盧偉聰在公共屋邨長大，憑努力學習，以優異成績入讀傳統名校喇沙書院，<span style=\"color: red;\">不但泳術出眾，奪魁無數</span>，而且早已展現領袖風範，歷任班長，後升讀港大，畢業後加入警隊。他小學時受祖父贈送的經典名著《三國演義》啟發，終令他矢志領導警隊除暴安良，成就了今日的「新一哥」。<br />\n<br />\n原來真係運動健將<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%96%87%E6%B2%99%E9%A3%9B%E9%AD%9A%E8%BA%8D%E7%99%BB%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A-%E5%93%A5-215512103.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2596%2587%25E6%25B2%2599%25E9%25A3%259B%25E9%25AD%259A%25E8%25BA%258D%25E7%2599%25BB%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A-%25E5%2593%25A5-215512103.html&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=f1a122b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%96%87%E6%B2%99%E9%A3%9B%E9%AD%9A%E8%BA%8D%E7%99%BB%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A-%E5%93%A5-215512103.html</a>"},{"pid":"93ae2385357e01a3e403a269a761e2e4f88f8d1f","tid":1321200,"uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:08:34.000Z","msg":"高質"},{"pid":"aa49aaf3e353b38194fe17dfbd753e93ebef15b5","tid":1321200,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93ae2385357e01a3e403a269a761e2e4f88f8d1f","tid":1321200,"uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:08:34.000Z","msg":"高質"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:21:29.000Z","msg":"多謝，出返去記得推重要post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6fb316614d80f336d4d3aaae3b0a3ff0438cbb","tid":1321200,"uid":69395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T11:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jZFgsP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jZFgsP.png&h=e977b90f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EnrgzeC.png\" data-thumbnail